Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:08.65,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,538)}與
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:08.65,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(633,538)}風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:08.65,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(705,538)}滿
